SimEntity.description: Controls the movements of the terrorists and issues attack orders to the terrorists it has selected. The cell also serves as a relay and registers it's terrorist, their sensors and their munitions. The terrorist cell must have a connection to the NauticalChart so that it understands the environment. The terrorists receive all of their information from the planner and report back at the end of their attack
SimEntity.name: TerroristCellPlanner
